Results and Findings¶

Insights Gained¶

  • Skill Gap Analysis - Users can identify areas to improve their qualifications for each occupation. This is useful for users who want to excel in their current occupation, or switch to a different occupation where they would be more qualified.

  • Salary Prediction - Provides users with a clear understanding of their earning potential. This section shows users what salay percentile they fall in for their occupation. THey can improve their earning potential by working on the skills they lack in using the skills difference tool.

  • Dynamic Visualizations - Using the occupation and industry insights dashboard, users can do in-depth anaylsis of their occupation and look at things like employment projections, education insights, AI suceptibility, and much more!
